{"tid":1064331,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[燎原火] 車太鉉,金俊浩 高爾夫賭博爭議","createTime":"2019-03-16T12:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T18:06:07.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f481e3d3b19db9ff526982fcc5d1f2c9c34f72","tid":1064331,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"3月16日播出的KBS 1TV《KBS新聞》中,鄭俊英等所屬的KBS 2TV《兩天一夜》成員的群組內容中,包含了部分出演人員打數百萬韓元賭球的情況。<br />\n<br />\n2016年7月1日,車太賢上傳了數十張5萬韓元紙鈔的照片,並炫耀這是和金俊浩打高爾夫後得到的錢。 他還留下了&quot;舉報就會被抓了&quot;,似乎知道自己的行為是不合法<br />\n<br />\n7月19日車太賢表示自己贏了225萬韓元,金俊浩贏了260萬韓元。 據推測,打賭的地點是泰國。 KBS方面表示:&quot;除了這個對話之外,隨處可見可以推測出他們經常打賭的內容。&quot;<br />\n<br />\nKBS方面還表示:&quot;當時該群組也有負責PD,但是沒有勸阻或忠告就默認了。特別是金俊浩在2009年因海外賭博引發爭議而中斷活動。並表示當時PD已離開KBS電視台。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"7e133f079bf730e13ca029316c5aef27e40fdb04","tid":1064331,"uid":46435,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"其實好小事"},{"pid":"0b78a4e6017b53ed124bb72e889fbc16ac3f6b7a","tid":1064331,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e133f079bf730e13ca029316c5aef27e40fdb04","tid":1064331,"uid":46435,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"其實好小事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"金俊浩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知會唔會玩撚完"},{"pid":"65631c600f093a310b53e5ca8ac1fc59ada76117","tid":1064331,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"犯咩法？"},{"pid":"3ec7624e9c0cc1b609f47ced65c8b0d68c94b968","tid":1064331,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:56:37.000Z","msg":"韓國人係海外都唔可以賭波?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173002b1f653503f64d328336c6c7d2ad3c08311","tid":1064331,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e133f079bf730e13ca029316c5aef27e40fdb04","tid":1064331,"uid":46435,"like":22,"dislik